  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety of 3% Minoxidil Lotion for Chest Hair Enhancement</brief_title>
  <official_title>Efficacy and Safety of 3% Minoxidil Lotion for Chest Hair Enhancement : A Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled Study</official_title>
